sources.title: They Call Me Jeeg (Full Movie) Action, Superhero, Dark Sci-Fi, HD
sources.description:
In "They Call Me Jeeg," Enzo, a lonely and misanthropic small time crook, uses the superpowers gained after falling in the Tiber river to chase down a crazy gangster called "The gypsy".

Director: Gabriele Mainetti
Writers: Nicola Guaglianone (story), Nicola Guaglianone (screenplay)
Stars: Claudio Santamaria, Luca Marinelli, Ilenia Pastorelli
2015
